flowchart TD
  S([TATA: gue ada project]):::start --> K[Nami + Lelouch:<br/>buka project + kickoff]
  K --> D[Lelouch + Senku:<br/>Discovery / Requirement]
  D --> DS[Sogeking+Bulma+Shikamaru+Saitama:<br/>Design awal]
  DS --> L{LOOP bangun bertahap}
  L --> R[Tata req fitur/revisi<br/>di tengah jalan]
  R --> RF[masuk ALUR REQUEST<br/>fitur LIVE]
  RF --> ST[Nami: update status + backlog]
  ST --> Q{App lengkap /<br/>Tata puas?}
  Q -->|Belum| R
  Q -->|Ya| QA[L: QA full regression]
  QA --> G[Kakashi: Pre-Tata Gate final]
  G --> GO[Levi: deploy / go-live]
  GO --> M[Nami: MoM penutup + retro]
  M --> E([APP JADI - LIVE & terdokumentasi]):::done
  classDef start fill:#a87fb8,color:#fff,stroke:#6b4779
  classDef done fill:#6b8454,color:#fff,stroke:#3f5230
